This is not a new thing, often various gods both light and dark have worked together for some common goal but this is different and worrying in two ways.
First the alliance is composed of many who had previously been at war, namely Orcus and Balrog who hate one another, to unify such long time opponents there must be such a prize for both that should make the forces of good and light very very worried.
Second the alliance obviously has some purpose, since I have been aware of this alliance Lolth , Balrog, Orcus and many other dark minions have been seen in all parts of the multiverse collecting rare minerals, magics and lore.

