@436=~Vecnas Evisiration~
@437=~Vecnas Evisiration
  (Metamagic)
  Level: 10
  Range: 60
  Duration: 5 rounds
  Casting Time: 5
  Area of Effect: Target creature
  Saving Throw: None
  
  Vecna one of the most talented and evil mages ever to inhabit the multiverse created this spell and even after his ascension to godhood it remained his favorite spell, it would amuse him to see the fear in enemies eyes as they died a slow very painful death being mercilessly cut apart by very sharp phantom blades. And often ,it is said, he would laugh with gusto when weak enemies would fall quickly and then their bodies be literally cut into small chunks.
  Effects:
  This spell creates a maelstrom of semi ethereal blades that attack the unfortunate victim of the spell, the blades will pass straight through any armor rematerializing just in time to slash and hack then slipping back into the near ethereal membrane. There is no protection from these blades as they pass straight through common spells such as Stoneskin, Protection from magical weapons etc... and are unaffected by magic resistance. But natural or magical effects which reduce slashing damage do apply since they toughen the entire body rather than act as a shield which the blades may pass through.
  The victim will suffer 10hp slashing damage twice per round for 5 rounds from the attacks of the blades, the attack will continue even after the victims death, the blades still doing their grizzly work  ~
@459=~Vecnas Star Portal~
@460=~Vecnas Star Portal
  (Metamagic)
  Level: 10
  Range: 60 
  Duration: instant
  Casting Time: 5
  Area of Effect: 250 radius
  Saving Throw: Half
  
  Vecna created this spell to combat powerful crteatures he faced on his many journys to alternate Prime Material Planes. By any definition it is a materpiece of magical script, and a masterwork on lateral thinking. This spell, like the 9th lv spell Gate, creates a gate between one place and another. One end of the gate is located within casting range of the spell, again as the Gate spell, the other end though instead of being created on one of the infernal planes ( and allowing infernal creatures to enter the prime ) is created on the corona of a meadium sized sun. The effect of this is dramatic, for a few seconds, before the massive energy transfer closes the gate, the full force of the stars heat,light,radiation,pressure and gravity blasts throgh the failing gate onto the targert location. Any beings caught within 40ft of the targert location will face the stars energy directly, with no save, all others within 250ft of the bast radius will get a saving throw for half dammage ( this includes the caster ).
  Effects:
  All within 40ft of the target location will take 20d10 crushing dammage, 15d10 fire dammage, will be poisoned for 6hp per round (untill cured) and be blinded for 1 turn.
  All others including the caster can save for half dammage, and are blinded for 2 rounds   ~
@461=~Vecnas PSR ( Pull down sky rock )~
@462=~Vecnas PSR ( Pull down sky rock )
  (Metamagic)
  Level: 10
  Range: 40 
  Duration: instant
  Casting Time: 5
  Area of Effect: 500 radius
  Saving Throw: None
  
  Effects:
  This hellish spell could only have been thought up by one as evil as vecna himself, casting it creates an immensly powerful telekinetic pull on any nearby sky rocks, those lumps of earth that pass by our round earth ball, some time after this spell has been cast, the asteroid will land on the location desired by the caster. All in the blast area suffer a huge ammount of crushing and stun dammage, are knocked uncocious, and deafened ( no save ) for 5 rounds. Those in the small 20ft eppicenter are killed instantly, with a save at -6 allowed  ~

